{"bookmarked": 8, "bucket_name": "Today", "bucket_order": 3, "change_log": [{"anon": "stud", "data": "jlmu1fka2r72mm", "type": "create", "uid_a": "a_0", "when": "2018-09-03T22:04:18Z"}, {"anon": "no", "to": "jlmu1fk5i5p2ml", "type": "followup", "uid": "ijbyyqoowfj720", "when": "2018-09-03T22:50:02Z"}, {"anon": "stud", "data": "jlo4ezoqnwh8m", "to": "jlmu1fk5i5p2ml", "type": "s_answer", "uid_a": "a_1", "when": "2018-09-04T19:42:33Z"}, {"anon": "no", "to": "jlmu1fk5i5p2ml", "type": "feedback", "uid": "ijkkcj71l3912c", "when": "2018-09-04T20:44:51Z"}, {"anon": "stud", "to": "jlmu1fk5i5p2ml", "type": "followup", "uid_a": "a_2", "when": "2018-09-05T19:19:44Z"}], "children": [{"anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Week 9/2 - 9/8", "bucket_order": 81, "children": [{"anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Week 9/2 - 9/8", "bucket_order": 81, "children": [], "config": {}, "created": "2018-09-04T20:44:51Z", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "id": "jlo6n40e7kc6ou", "subject": "Additionally, companies in industries like gaming (in my experience) put more weight on cover letters/often require them and may reference them in your interview", "tag_good": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "type": "feedback", "uid": "ijkkcj71l3912c", "updated": "2018-09-04T20:44:51Z"}], "config": {}, "created": "2018-09-03T22:50:02Z", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "id": "jlmvo96mlif3tj", "no_answer": 0, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "<p>I don&#39;t have any evidence to support this, but I would think that cover letters might make more of a difference for smaller companies (e.g., startups). So maybe writing short cover letters for smaller companies (and no cover letters for larger companies) is a more optimal use of time.</p>", "tag_good": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "type": "followup", "uid": "ijbyyqoowfj720", "updated": "2018-09-03T22:50:02Z"}, {"bucket_name": "Today", "bucket_order": 3, "children": [], "config": {}, "created": "2018-09-04T19:42:32Z", "data": {"embed_links": []}, "folders": [], "history": [{"anon": "stud", "content": "<p>Much the same way you&#39;re applying to hundreds of companies, recruiters are evaluating hundreds of applications. My sense is that it matters little - it depends how close you are to the margin.</p>", "created": "2018-09-04T19:42:33Z", "subject": "", "uid_a": "a_1"}], "id": "jlo4ezoedn78l", "is_tag_endorse": false, "tag_endorse": [{"admin": false, "class_sections": ["classof2019_hyq0br1u3kx7dg"], "endorser": {"jqq5rhyduky27b": 1552968432}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "icguy14uq1n1lc", "name": "Charlie Tian", "photo": null, "photo_url": null, "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}, {"admin": false, "endorser": {}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "is6p9s6omub10j", "name": "Jeanelle Wu", "photo": null, "photo_url": null, "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}, {"admin": false, "endorser": {}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "j6d4undmzeh69g", "name": "Shivin Devgon", "photo": "1553216198_35.png", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/j6d4undmzeh69g/1553216198_35.png", "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}], "tag_endorse_arr": ["icguy14uq1n1lc", "is6p9s6omub10j", "j6d4undmzeh69g"], "type": "s_answer"}, {"anon": "stud", "bucket_name": "Week 9/2 - 9/8", "bucket_order": 81, "children": [], "config": {}, "created": "2018-09-05T19:19:44Z", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "id": "jlpj1i1d9ox460", "no_answer": 0, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "I do recruiting for a startup. Almost no applicants submit a cover letter. Almost any applicant who submitted a cover letter that demonstrates:<div>i) a good understanding of the role/company</div><div>ii) that they\u2019re qualified to do the role well</div><div>will get an interview and a huge leg up throughout the hiring process because it shows that they\u2019re dedicated to our company/mission.\u00a0</div>", "tag_good": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "type": "followup", "uid_a": "a_2", "updated": "2018-09-05T19:19:44Z"}], "config": {}, "created": "2018-09-03T22:04:18Z", "data": {"embed_links": []}, "default_anonymity": "no", "drafts": null, "folders": ["peer_directed", "other"], "history": [{"anon": "stud", "content": "<p>2nd year here, going through that time-honored tradition of desperately applying to all the internships ever in the hopes I&#39;ll eventually land one :&#39;)</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>I know the traditional advice is\u00a0to write a tailored cover letter for each company that lets you submit one. Unfortunately, cover letters, for me, are the most time-consuming part of the application and I find it hard to make it sound like I&#39;m genuinely passionate about the company (because I&#39;m really not, all I\u00a0want is\u00a0a job... I&#39;m sorry but I think most applicants will feel the same). Couple that with the fact that you generally need to send out a couple hundred apps to get a handful of interviews, and writing custom cover letters for ALL of them is simply impractical. There&#39;s just no time...</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>I understand that spending the effort on a cover letter can mean a lot to a company, which could improve my chances, but I think at this stage quantity is more important than quality. Any thoughts?</p>", "created": "2018-09-03T22:04:18Z", "subject": "How important are cover letters, really?", "uid_a": "a_0"}], "i_edits": [], "id": "jlmu1fk5i5p2ml", "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "my_favorite": false, "no_answer": 0, "no_answer_followup": 0, "nr": 7581, "num_favorites": 5, "q_edits": [], "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "s_edits": [], "status": "active", "t": 1654548648842, "tag_good": [{"admin": false, "endorser": {}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "iy0slp1n9kt3u9", "name": "Jason Zhou", "photo": "1548118179_35.png", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/iy0slp1n9kt3u9/1548118179_35.png", "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}, {"admin": false, "endorser": {}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "is6p6j9n6u55fp", "name": "Katie Gu", "photo": "1513749563_35.png", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/is6p6j9n6u55fp/1513749563_35.png", "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}, {"admin": false, "endorser": {}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "j5x7odf43ze772", "name": "Dhanush Patel", "photo": "1503736904_35.png", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/j5x7odf43ze772/1503736904_35.png", "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}, {"admin": false, "endorser": {}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "idgol4efpji4z6", "name": "Adam Victor", "photo": null, "photo_url": null, "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}, {"admin": false, "class_sections": ["classof2019_hyq0br1u3kx7dg"], "endorser": {"jqq5rhyduky27b": 1552968432}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "icguy14uq1n1lc", "name": "Charlie Tian", "photo": null, "photo_url": null, "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}, {"admin": false, "endorser": {}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "j6d4undmzeh69g", "name": "Shivin Devgon", "photo": "1553216198_35.png", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/j6d4undmzeh69g/1553216198_35.png", "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}, {"admin": false, "endorser": {}, "facebook_id": null, "id": "is6p6nezwwv5jd", "name": "Aryana Shabestari", "photo": null, "photo_url": null, "published": true, "role": "student", "us": false}], "tag_good_arr": ["iy0slp1n9kt3u9", "is6p6j9n6u55fp", "j5x7odf43ze772", "idgol4efpji4z6", "icguy14uq1n1lc", "j6d4undmzeh69g", "is6p6nezwwv5jd"], "tags": ["other", "peer_directed", "student"], "type": "question", "unique_views": 687}